articles.description: No. 3 Villanova has thrived on the 3 during its dominating Big East run, but the triple abandoned the Wildcats again in Wednesday's loss to Providence.

videos.description: Alan Herndon gets a steal leading to an Louis Adams layup plus a foul on the other end.

videos.headline: Cody Martin sets up his brother Caleb for dunk

videos.description: Justin James shows off his range and hits a 3-pointer from way out for Wyoming.
videos.headline: James drains deep 3- pointer

videos.description: Cody Martin's nice pass leads to Lindsey Drew's up-and-under layup plus a foul for Nevada.
